Package: nhlscrape
Type: Package
Title: Scrapes the NHL API and HTML reports to generate a database for statistical analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Adam Azoulay [aut, cre]
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Adam Azoulay <adam1azoulay@gmail.com> [aut, cre]"
  ))
Maintainer: Adam Azoulay <adam1azoulay@gmail.com>
URL: https://github.com/adamazoulay/nhlscrape
BugReports: https://github.com/adamazoulay/nhlscrape/issues
Description: Add game events to the database file to use for statistical analysis of hockey games. This means we only call the API
once for each game we add, and we have very fast retrieval of data once games have been added since the data is stored locally. 
